    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Sergei Markoff</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sergei.markoff\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/4/42/SergeiMarkoff.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:SergeiMarkoff.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sergei S. Markoff <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Sergei S. Markoff</b>, <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br />\na Russian computer scientist, computer chess and games programmer. He is author of the chess program <a href=\"/SmarThink\" title=\"SmarThink\">SmarThink</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. In 2003 Sergei introduced the <a href=\"/Botvinnik-Markoff_Extension\" title=\"Botvinnik-Markoff Extension\">Botvinnik-Markoff Extension</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. Sergei working in Sberbank leading a workgroup that focused on development of bank AI/ML systems especially in the area of speech technologies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=252677\">PASSED_PAWN_PUSH extension scheme (and SmarThink)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn_Extensions\" title=\"Passed Pawn Extensions\">Passed Pawn Extensions</a>, <a href=\"/SmarThink\" title=\"SmarThink\">SmarThink</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=299987\">Markoff - Botvinnik - Kaissa - Hsu - ABC - Berliner</a> by <a href=\"/Walter_Faxon\" title=\"Walter Faxon\">Walter Faxon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 09, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=318833\">The \"same threat extension\" as effective way to resolve horizon problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Botvinnik-Markoff_Extension\" title=\"Botvinnik-Markoff Extension\">Botvinnik-Markoff Extension</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=352384\">Forward pruning and some related techniques</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=353798\">Search behavior in a case of root fail high/low</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 10, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a>, <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=389135\">Forward/HB/Null move pruning ideas</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=389134\">Authors of Kaissa on quiscence search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 26, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Kaissa\" title=\"Kaissa\">Kaissa</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=470647\">Secrets of Rybka and Fruit from my point of view</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 15, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a>, <a href=\"/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29681\">A way to improve PVS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40385\">c# for chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40384\">Breadth-first search: revisiting</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40388\">Repetitions/50 moves and TT</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a>, <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45264\">Probabilistic approach to optimize search tree</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 22, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50294\">PSQ tables depending on king sides, pawn patterns etc.</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 01, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Piece-Square_tables&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Piece-Square tables (page does not exist)\">Piece-Square tables</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50512\">Improved history heuristic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 16, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50907\">Pruning in PV nodes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Reductions\" title=\"Reductions\">Reductions</a>, <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">Root</a>, <a href=\"/Node_Types\" title=\"Node Types\">Node Types</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51284\">Fail soft vs fail hard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Hard\" title=\"Fail-Hard\">Fail-Hard</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a>, <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58771\">SmarThink v1.80 is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55696&amp;start=108\">Re: txt: automated chess engine tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63847\">New SmarThink website</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66775\">Feed bayeselo with pure game results without PGN</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70723\">The Plan-9 to finally solve chess&#160;:)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70939\">The mystery of Alex Bernstein</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 06, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Alex_Bernstein\" title=\"Alex Bernstein\">Alex Bernstein</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70940\">Widely unknown pioneering chess \"paper machine\" by Gunter Sсhliebs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sergei S. Markoff</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 06, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://markoff.science/\">Sergei S. Markoff homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://independent.academia.edu/SergeiMarkoff\">Sergei S. Markoff academia.edu page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sergei.markoff\">Sergei Markoff - Facebook</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://smarthink.ru/\">SmarThink site</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/smarthink.htm\">SmarThink by Sergei Markoff, Russia - sdchesss.ru</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mobygames.com/developer/sheet/view/by_title/developerId,223424/\">Sergei Markoff</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mobygames.com/home\">mobygames</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sergei_Markoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sergei.markoff\">Sergei Markoff - Facebook</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Due to different, but equally valid ways of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transliteration\">transliterating</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyrillic_alphabet\">Cyrillic</a>, also <b>Sergei Markov</b>, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markov_number\">Markov number from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/smarthink.htm\">SmarThink by Sergei Markoff, Russia</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sdchess.ru/\">sdchess.ru</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aigroup.narod.ru/detailse.htm\">Some SmarThink details</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=318833\">The \"same threat extension\" as effective way to resolve horizon problem</a>, Sergei Markoff introduced the extension, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2003</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ru.linkedin.com/pub/sergei-markoff/2b/94/360?trk=pub-pbmap\">Sergei Markoff - Russian Federation | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div> \n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228225016\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 115/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 242/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4337-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228225016 and revision id 12561\n -->\n"
